232
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:25,020
Nhưng chỉ là hợp tác thôi đấy.

233
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:26,640
Chúng ta rõ chứ?

234
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:27,700
Nah.

235
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:31,920
Oi, Zoro.

236
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:32,890
